<bibRefCitation id="420E4B58FFA9FFCEFEE5143AFE63D912" author="QUATE L. W. &amp; BROWN B. V." box="[267,477,339,358]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" pagination="1 - 117" refId="ref5187" refString="QUATE L. W. &amp; BROWN B. V. 2004. Revision of Neotropical Setomimini (Diptera: Psychodidae: Psychodinae). Contributions in Science, Natural History Museum of Los Angeles County 500: 1 - 117." type="journal article" year="2004">QUATE &amp; BROWN (2004)</bibRefCitation>
